 is obscure). The name was introduced to England by  Eleanor of Aquitaine  (  1122–1204 ), who came from Aquitaine in south-west France to be the wife of  King Henry II . It was also borne by Eleanor of Provence, the wife of  Henry III , and Eleanor of Castile, wife of  Edward I ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Ellen Moriss was born in 1450, in England, United Kingdom. She married Sir William Stover in September 1481, in England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter. She died on 16 March 1485, in her hometown, at the age of 35."},"et":{"1450–16 Mar 1485":"1450–16. märts 1485","1450–1494":"1450–1494","1469–1540":"1469–1540","1450–1485":"1450–1485","1469":"1469","Sep 1481":"september 1481","16 Mar 1485":"16. märts 1485","1485":"1485","1540":"1540","1450":"1450","1494":"1494","Oxfordshire, England":"Oxfordshire, England","England":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1450–16 Mar 1485":"1450–16. maaliskuuta 1485","1450–1494":"1450–1494","1469–1540":"1469–1540","1450–1485":"1450–1485","1469":"1469","Sep 1481":"syyskuu 1481","16 Mar 1485":"16. maaliskuuta 1485","1485":"1485","1540":"1540","1450":"1450","1494":"1494","Oxfordshire, England":"Oxfordshire, England","England":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1450–16 Mar 1485":"1450–16 mars 1485","1450–1494":"1450–1494","1469–1540":"1469–1540","1450–1485":"1450–1485","1469":"1469","Sep 1481":"septembre 1481","16 Mar 1485":"16 mars 1485","1485":"1485","1540":"1540","1450":"1450","1494":"1494","Oxfordshire, England":"Oxfordshire, Angleterre","England":"Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Ellen Moriss est née en 1450, à Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a épousé Sir William Stover en septembre 1481, à Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fille. Elle est décédée le 16 mars 1485, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 35 ans."},"de":{"1450–16 Mar 1485":"1450–16. März 1485","1450–1494":"1450–1494","1469–1540":"1469–1540","1450–1485":"1450–1485","1469":"1469","Sep 1481":"September 1481","16 Mar 1485":"16. 